data.description: Welcome to 425 Spencer Landing W. This very spacious home is located in the sought after subdivision of Spencer Landing on a cul de sac lot. Step inside to discover an open concept living space with plenty of natural light. Relax and unwind in the spacious primary suite, complete with a newly updated ensuite bathroom. His and hers vanities and walk in closets. The additional bedrooms offer plenty of space and large closets for you or guests. Conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping centers. You truly do have to see this space to believe its size.
